    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理称满载爆炸物的大篷车为恐怖主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/australian-pm-labels-caravan-packed-with-explosives-as-terrorism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯表示，在悉尼远郊发现一辆装满爆炸物的大篷车是恐怖主义阴谋的一部分，当地官员认为这一发现与最近发生的一系列反犹太袭击事件有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/australian-pm-labels-caravan-packed-with-explosives-as-terrorism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 23:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 将支付 2500 万美元以结束特朗普因 1 月 6 日禁令而提起的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/meta-to-pay-25-million-to-end-trump-lawsuit-over-jan-6-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统的一名律师表示，Meta Platforms Inc. 同意支付 2500 万美元以解决唐纳德·特朗普的指控，即在 2021 年 1 月 6 日美国国会大厦发生骚乱后，禁止他进入该公司的社交媒体网络是非法审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/meta-to-pay-25-million-to-end-trump-lawsuit-over-jan-6-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 22:53:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利国会最终批准长期寻求的养老金改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/chile-congress-gives-final-backing-to-long-sought-pension-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利国会最终批准了一项改革，该改革将提高当前和未来退休人员的养老金，在政府做出重大让步之后，总统加布里埃尔·博里奇只获得了部分胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/chile-congress-gives-final-backing-to-long-sought-pension-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 22:51:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称美联储在银行监管方面做得“很糟糕”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-says-fed-has-done-terrible-job-on-banking-regulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普严厉批评美联储的银行监管方式，并指责美联储主席杰伊·鲍威尔在抗击通胀方面失误，同时避免直接对利率发表评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-says-fed-has-done-terrible-job-on-banking-regulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 21:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《纽约时报》称特朗普司法部考虑撤销针对纽约市长的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-doj-weighs-dropping-case-against-nyc-mayor-adams-nyt-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《纽约时报》援引知情人士的话称，司法部官员已经与曼哈顿检察官讨论撤销对纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯的腐败指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-doj-weighs-dropping-case-against-nyc-mayor-adams-nyt-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 21:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前参议员梅内德斯因金条贿赂案被判 11 年有期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ex-senator-bob-menendez-gets-11-years-for-gold-bar-bribe-scheme</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲍勃·梅嫩德斯因充当埃及的外国代理人并收受金条和其他贿赂而被判处 11 年监禁，检察官称这可能是有史以来美国参议员最严重的腐败案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ex-senator-bob-menendez-gets-11-years-for-gold-bar-bribe-scheme</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:44:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫考虑采取数十种新方法来夺取支出权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-eyes-fight-with-congress-courts-over-spending-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份文件显示，白宫正在考虑挑战一项已有 50 年历史的法律的合宪性，该法律限制了总统对联邦支出的控制、放松了公务员的解雇、限制了薪酬并控制了独立机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-eyes-fight-with-congress-courts-over-spending-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:33:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普撤销引发混乱的支出冻结令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-reverses-spending-freeze-order-that-sparked-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统撤销了冻结一系列联邦拨款、贷款和财政援助的命令 — — 这是在政府和非营利组织经历数日的不确定性和焦虑之后发生的戏剧性逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-reverses-spending-freeze-order-that-sparked-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢特尼克称特朗普关税将恢复美国经济并赢得尊重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/lutnick-says-mexico-canada-can-avoid-tariffs-with-border-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普提名的商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克 (Howard Lutnick) 在确认听证会上为关税问题做出了详细的辩护，这是迄今为止内阁人选发出的最明确信号，表明新政府准备对盟友和对手征收关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/lutnick-says-mexico-canada-can-avoid-tariffs-with-border-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 17:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普想要“扣押”国会拨款。这意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/impoundment-can-trump-really-refuse-to-spend-money-congress-appropriated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[扣押资金之争已经打响。特朗普总统试图在华盛顿实施其意志的方式之一就是拒绝花掉国会要求他花掉的所有资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/impoundment-can-trump-really-refuse-to-spend-money-congress-appropriated</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 17:02:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
